channel.title: Looking for a coder, Setting up new server!
channel.description:
Hi, I am looking for a Coder that has a good knowledge and maturity. I already have a playerbase of 1500+ and the funds to buy a VPS. This is a 50% share in the server. For more info please contact me on skype: tim.craft888
What you need to qualify: Good knowledge of Java, C#. Time to help out.
Cheers.
